Cloud vs Ollama

| ChatGPT             | Ollama                                                        |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Internet required   | Can work offline                                              |
| Uses OpenAI servers | Runs on your computer                                         |
| API cost            | Free after downloading the model (hardware costs still apply) |
| Data leaves your PC | Data stays local                                              |
| Easy to use         | Requires installation                                         |


