==========

In One Sentence
Llama is the AI model (the brain) that understands and generates language.
Ollama is the local runtime (the engine/player) that downloads, manages, and runs AI models like Llama on your own computer.

For your current AI Meeting Notes Summarizer, replacing a cloud API (such as Gemini) with Ollama + Llama 3 would let the application generate summaries locally,
which can reduce ongoing API costs and help keep sensitive meeting data on your own machine or organization's servers.

